---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../components/SectionDivider.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Voice Workshops & Group Training"
  description="Bring expert voice training to your organization. Workshops on vocal health, communication skills, and ensemble techniques for groups in the Pacific Northwest."
  ogImage="/images/og/og-workshops.jpg"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container reveal">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Workshops' }]} />
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Workshops & Presentations</span>
      <h1>Teaching Voice from the Inside Out</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Interactive workshops that help singers and speakers understand how the voice actually works — so they can use it with greater confidence, clarity, and purpose.</p>
      <p class="hero-body">I offer educational workshops for groups, organizations, and events. Whether you're looking for a featured session at your conference, a retreat experience for your choir, or a structured series for your team, I bring the same approach: clear frameworks, hands-on exploration, and practical understanding that participants carry forward.</p>
      <a href="#workshop-inquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Bring Me to Your Event</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider variant="wave" topColor="var(--color-navy-deep)" bottomColor="var(--color-white)" />

  <!-- Answer Capsule — structured summary for AI search engines -->
  <section class="capsule-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="answer-capsule">Ted's Voice Academy offers interactive voice workshops for organizations, conferences, and retreats. The signature AVF™ Workshop Series teaches how the voice works through the Adaptive Voice Framework™, with separate paths for singers and speakers. Custom workshops available for choirs, professional teams, and educational events.</p>
      <p class="page-date">Last updated: <time datetime="2026-02-05">February 5, 2026</time></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AVF Workshop Series Section -->
  <section class="avf-series-section">
    <div class="container container-narrow reveal">
      <div class="series-intro-grid">
        <div class="series-intro-text">
          <h2>The AVF™ Workshop Series</h2>
          <p>This is my signature educational offering — a live, in-person workshop series grounded in the <a href="/avf">Adaptive Voice Framework (AVF)</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="series-intro-image">
          <img src="/images/ted-workshop-teaching.webp" alt="Ted Chamberlain teaching in his voice studio, gesturing while explaining vocal technique" class="series-photo" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>The series begins with a shared session for all participants, then continues in two focused paths: one for singers, one for speakers. Each path includes three workshops total (including the shared first session), with each session lasting two hours.</p>

      <h3>What participants experience:</h3>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>A clear, system-level understanding of how the voice works</li>
        <li>Hands-on exploration of the Five Pillars and Eight Dials</li>
        <li>Practical awareness they can apply immediately</li>
        <li>Language for describing and developing their own voice</li>
        <li>Confidence in using their voice across varied contexts</li>
      </ul>

      <p>The series is designed with a low floor and high ceiling — accessible to beginners while remaining valuable for experienced singers and speakers.</p>
      <p>Every participant receives a copy of <em>AVF: The Adaptive Voice Framework</em> as part of the experience. The book serves as a shared reference during workshops and a resource for continued learning afterward.</p>
      <p><strong>For speakers:</strong> The speaking path integrates the <a href="/pass-profile">PASS Profile™</a> — my proprietary communication assessment that maps how each participant naturally communicates. This adds personalized insight and language that supports intentional, authentic speaking.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bring the Series / Public Dates -->
  <section class="series-details-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="details-grid reveal-stagger">
        <div class="detail-card reveal">
          <h3>Bring the Series to Your Organization</h3>
          <p>The AVF Workshop Series can be delivered as a private experience for your group, retreat, or event. I'll work with you to adapt the format to your needs while maintaining the core learning arc.</p>
          <a href="#workshop-inquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Inquire About a Private Series</a>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card reveal">
          <h3>Public Workshop Dates</h3>
          <p>I'll be announcing public workshop dates soon. If you'd like to be notified when registration opens, let me know.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Join the Interest List</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider variant="curve" topColor="var(--color-white)" bottomColor="var(--color-navy-deep)" />

  <!-- Conference Sessions Section -->
  <section class="conference-section">
    <div class="container container-narrow reveal">
      <h2>Conference Sessions & Vocal Education Events</h2>
      <p>I'm available for invited teaching at conferences, harmony schools, and vocal education events. Past and current contexts include events like Harmony College Northwest, Harmony University, and professional voice conferences.</p>

      <h3>What I bring:</h3>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>A clear, practical approach to understanding how the voice works</li>
        <li>Content shaped to fit your audience and event goals</li>
        <li>Sessions that are both useful and enjoyable to attend</li>
        <li>Tools and ideas participants can put to use right away</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Sessions can range from a single breakout to multi-session intensives. I'm happy to discuss what would serve your event best.</p>
      <a href="#workshop-inquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Invite Me to Your Event</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider variant="wave" topColor="var(--color-navy-deep)" bottomColor="var(--color-off-white)" />

  <!-- Custom Workshops Section -->
  <section class="custom-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="reveal">Custom Workshops for Groups & Teams</h2>
      <p class="section-intro reveal">Looking to bring voice education to your chorus, quartet, team, or organization? I design custom workshops tailored to your group's focus and goals.</p>

      <div class="custom-grid reveal-stagger">
        <div class="custom-card reveal">
          <h3><svg class="icon-inline" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>For singers and ensembles:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Building a strong foundation: breath, tone, unity, and healthy singing habits</li>
            <li>Understanding the voice as a balanced, responsive system</li>
            <li>Leveling up: moving beyond "correct" into expressive, artistic singing</li>
            <li>Performance skills and stage presence</li>
            <li>Genuine engagement and authentic performance</li>
            <li>Musicality and artistry that connects with audiences</li>
            <li>Vocal health and sustainable singing</li>
            <li>Warm-up design and daily practice frameworks</li>
            <li>How to run an effective sectional rehearsal (for section leaders and directors)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-card reveal">
          <h3><svg class="icon-inline" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/></svg>For speakers and professional teams:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Communication style awareness featuring the PASS Profile</li>
            <li>Developing your own speaking style and personal voice brand</li>
            <li><a href="/speaking">Speaking with confidence and authenticity</a></li>
            <li>Expressive clarity for presenters and leaders</li>
            <li>Voice use in professional settings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="custom-contexts">These workshops work well for choir retreats, quartet coaching intensives, leadership teams, professional development days, and organizational offsites.</p>
      <div class="custom-cta">
        <a href="#workshop-inquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Let's Design Something Together</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Workshop Inquiry Form Section -->
  <section id="workshop-inquiry" class="inquiry-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="inquiry-grid">
        <div class="inquiry-form-column reveal-left">
          <h2>Let's Talk About Your Event</h2>
          <p class="inquiry-intro">Whether you're planning a conference session, a choir retreat, or a team development experience, I'd enjoy hearing what you have in mind.</p>

          <form
            name="workshop-inquiry"
            method="POST"
            action="/success"
            data-netlify="true"
            netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
            class="inquiry-form"
          >
            <p class="hidden">
              <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
            </p>
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="workshop-inquiry" />

            <!-- Contact Name -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="contact-name">Contact name <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="contact-name" required />
            </div>

            <!-- Organization -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="organization">Organization <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="organization" name="organization" required />
            </div>

            <!-- Email -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email address <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
            </div>

            <!-- Phone -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone number (optional)</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" />
            </div>

            <!-- Workshop Interest -->
            <fieldset class="form-group">
              <legend>Workshop interest <span class="required">*</span></legend>
              <div class="checkbox-group">
                <label class="checkbox-label">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="workshop-interest[]" value="vocal-health" />
                  <span>Vocal Health for Professionals</span>
                </label>
                <label class="checkbox-label">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="workshop-interest[]" value="communication" />
                  <span>Communication & Presence</span>
                </label>
                <label class="checkbox-label">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="workshop-interest[]" value="team-voice" />
                  <span>Team Voice (ensemble/choir)</span>
                </label>
                <label class="checkbox-label">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="workshop-interest[]" value="custom" />
                  <span>Custom Workshop</span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </fieldset>

            <!-- Group Size -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="group-size">Group size <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <select id="group-size" name="group-size" required>
                <option value="">Select group size</option>
                <option value="small">Small (5–15 people)</option>
                <option value="medium">Medium (15–30 people)</option>
                <option value="large">Large (30–50 people)</option>
                <option value="very-large">Very Large (50+)</option>
                <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <!-- Preferred Timeframe -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="timeframe">Preferred timeframe (optional)</label>
              <input type="text" id="timeframe" name="timeframe" placeholder="e.g., Spring 2026, flexible" />
            </div>

            <!-- Tell Me More -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="details">Tell me more about what you have in mind <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <textarea id="details" name="details" rows="4" required></textarea>
            </div>

            <!-- Submit -->
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Inquiry</button>
          </form>
        </div>

        <div class="inquiry-info-column reveal-right">
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>What happens next</h3>
            <p>After you submit this form:</p>
            <ol class="expect-list">
              <li>I'll review your inquiry and respond within 24–48 hours.</li>
              <li>We'll have a conversation about your event, your group, and your goals.</li>
              <li>I'll put together a tailored proposal for your consideration.</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card info-card-accent">
            <h3>Prefer to reach out directly?</h3>
            <div class="contact-method">
              <h4>Email</h4>
              <a href="mailto:ted@tedsvoiceacademy.com">ted@tedsvoiceacademy.com</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-method">
              <h4>Phone</h4>
              <a href="tel:+12534142267">253-414-2267</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    background:
      url('/images/noise-texture.png') repeat,
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy-deep) 0%, var(--color-navy-medium) 100%);
    background-size: 200px 200px, 100% 100%;
    background-blend-mode: soft-light, normal;
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw + 1rem, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border: none;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-gold-bright);
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-gold-hover);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(212, 168, 75, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gold-bright);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-gold-bright);
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
  }

  /* Container Narrow */
  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Series Intro Grid */
  .series-intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .series-intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .series-photo {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* AVF Series Section */
  .avf-series-section {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .avf-series-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 1rem, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .avf-series-section h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .avf-series-section p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .avf-series-section a {
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .avf-series-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .avf-series-section strong {
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
  }

  .avf-series-section em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .feature-list {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Series Details Section */
  .series-details-section {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .details-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .details-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .detail-card {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold-bright);
  }

  .detail-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .detail-card p {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Conference Section */
  .conference-section {
    background:
      url('/images/noise-texture.png') repeat,
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy-deep) 0%, var(--color-navy-medium) 100%);
    background-size: 200px 200px, 100% 100%;
    background-blend-mode: soft-light, normal;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .conference-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 1rem, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .conference-section h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .conference-section p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .conference-section .feature-list li {
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .conference-section .btn-primary {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  /* Custom Workshops Section */
  .custom-section {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .custom-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 1rem, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .custom-section .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  .custom-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .custom-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .custom-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold-bright);
  }

  .custom-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .custom-card ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .custom-card li {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .custom-card li a {
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .custom-card li a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .custom-contexts {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 2rem auto 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .custom-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Workshop Inquiry Form Section */
  .inquiry-section {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .inquiry-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .inquiry-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .inquiry-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 1rem, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .inquiry-intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Form Styles */
  .inquiry-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-group label,
  .form-group legend {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  fieldset.form-group {
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .required {
    color: var(--color-gold-bright);
  }

  input[type="text"],
  input[type="email"],
  input[type="tel"],
  select,
  textarea {
    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid #e0ddd5;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  input:focus,
  select:focus,
  textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-gold-bright);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212, 168, 75, 0.15);
  }

  textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 100px;
  }

  .checkbox-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .checkbox-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .checkbox-label input {
    width: 1.125rem;
    height: 1.125rem;
    accent-color: var(--color-gold-bright);
  }

  .hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Info Column */
  .inquiry-info-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .info-card {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .info-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy-deep);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .info-card p {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .expect-list {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  .expect-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Accent Card */
  .info-card-accent {
